string.text: This computer skills check helps you to assess your computer skills. You will get an indication on what you are capable of and what you can improve.
Click to listen to the text
Advice and tips on how to get better
Look through your answers in the test
You have assessed yourself on level 3 out of 3 in this check.
Digital skills on level 3 mean that you are a reflected user of more complex digital tools and services. The development within digital skills is fast and it is wise to keep yourself updated.
You have assessed yourself on level 2 out of 3 in this check.
Digital skills on level 2 mean that you can relate actively to digital information and can use information in new contexts and situations. You know several digital tools and services and use them.
You have assessed yourself on level 1 out of 3 levels in this check.
Digital skills on level 1 mean that you can relate to digital information whenever this is necessary and use simple digital tools.
